Company Overview of Hirtle, Callaghan & Co., LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hirtle, Callaghan & Co., LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to Individuals. It also caters to high net worth individuals, banking or thrift institutions, Investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, education institutions, trusts, family offices, endowments, foundations, healthcare organizations, and pension and profit sharing plans. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It also manages mutual funds and hedge funds. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. Its alternative investments include investment in hedge funds and private equity markets. The firm empl...
Hirtle, Callaghan & Co., LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to Individuals. It also caters to high net worth individuals, banking or thrift institutions, Investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, education institutions, trusts, family offices, endowments, foundations, healthcare organizations, and pension and profit sharing plans. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It also manages mutual funds and hedge funds. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. Its alternative investments include investment in hedge funds and private equity markets. The firm employs multiple strategies in the private equity space including venture, buy out, and distressed to make its investments. It employs fundamental analysis along top-down approach to make its investments. The firm conducts extensive in-house research to make its investments. Hirtle, Callaghan & Co., LLC was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in West Conshohocken, Pennsylvania with additional offices in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania; Scottsdale, Arizona; New York, New York; Chicago, Illinois; and Atlanta, Georgia.
