Hirtle Callaghan & Co Has Trimmed Gamestop (GME) Stake, Point72 Asia Hong Kong LTD Increased Grace W R & Co Del New (GRA) Holding


					
						July 28, 2017 - By Migdalia James

Point72 Asia Hong Kong Ltd increased Grace W R & Co Del New (GRA) stake by 1143.8% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Point72 Asia Hong Kong Ltd acquired 5,719 shares as Grace W R & Co Del New (GRA)’s stock declined 0.67%. The Point72 Asia Hong Kong Ltd holds 6,219 shares with $421,000 value, up from 500 last quarter. Grace W R & Co Del New now has $4.77B valuation. The stock decreased 2.17% or $1.55 during the last trading session, reaching $69.82. About shares traded. W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA) has declined 6.22% since July 28, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 22.92% the S&P500.







Hirtle Callaghan & Co Llc decreased Gamestop Corp (GME) stake by 98.47% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Hirtle Callaghan & Co Llc sold 965 shares as Gamestop Corp (GME)’s stock declined 5.28%. The Hirtle Callaghan & Co Llc holds 15 shares with $16,000 value, down from 980 last quarter. Gamestop Corp now has $2.20B valuation. The stock increased 3.14% or $0.66 during the last trading session, reaching $21.7. About shares traded. GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME) has declined 15.17% since July 28, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 31.87% the S&P500.
Since February 21, 2017, it had 1 insider buy, and 4 selling transactions for $8.19 million activity. The insider Dockman William C. sold $345,919. Shelnitz Mark A sold $1.92M worth of stock. 3,750 W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA) shares with value of $263,813 were bought by Blaser Thomas E. Shares for $5.76M were sold by FESTA ALFRED E.
Among 11 analysts covering W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA), 6 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 5 Hold. Therefore 55% are positive. W. R. Grace & Co had 19 analyst reports since August 3, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The rating was maintained by Macquarie Research with “Outperform” on Monday, March 7. The firm earned “Neutral” rating on Thursday, June 8 by Goldman Sachs. The firm has “Buy” rating by Monness Crespi given on Thursday, April 28. As per Tuesday, September 13, the company rating was initiated by Seaport Global Securities. Goldman Sachs upgraded W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA) on Monday, December 12 to “Buy” rating. The stock has “Neutral” rating by Goldman Sachs on Monday, March 14. On Wednesday, November 30 the stock rating was downgraded by Jefferies to “Hold”. As per Thursday, December 10, the company rating was initiated by BB&T Capital. Robert W. Baird upgraded W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA) rating on Tuesday, February 7. Robert W. Baird has “Outperform” rating and $85 target. Seaport Global Securities upgraded W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA) on Tuesday, November 1 to “Buy” rating.
Point72 Asia Hong Kong Ltd decreased Wal (NYSE:WMT) stake by 13,881 shares to 9,300 valued at $643,000 in 2016Q4. It also reduced Veeva Sys Inc (NYSE:VEEV) stake by 40,352 shares and now owns 3,451 shares. Total Sys Svcs Inc (NYSE:TSS) was reduced too. 
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.88 in Q4 2016. Its down 0.04, from 0.92 in 2016Q3. It dropped, as 46 investors sold GRA shares while 91 reduced holdings. 36 funds opened positions while 84 raised stakes. 56.49 million shares or 1.59% less from 57.40 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Profund Advisors Limited Liability Corp, a Maryland-based fund reported 5,658 shares. 3,191 are held by Royal Bancorp Of Canada. American Intl Grp Inc Inc accumulated 1,854 shares. Oxford Asset, United Kingdom-based fund reported 134,704 shares. D E Shaw And Communications has 1.08 million shares. Trexquant Ltd Partnership accumulated 0.15% or 13,737 shares. Moreover, Robeco Institutional Asset Mngmt Bv has 0.01% invested in W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA). Cipher LP owns 47,130 shares for 0.21% of their portfolio. Nbt Bank & Trust N A New York holds 0.07% of its portfolio in W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA) for 6,000 shares. Ent Finance Ser Corporation has 0% invested in W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA) for 38 shares. Citigroup Inc holds 152,456 shares. Geode Capital Mgmt Lc invested in 492,426 shares or 0.02% of the stock. 75,668 are owned by Rhumbline Advisers. Weiss Asset Limited Partnership has invested 0.03% of its portfolio in W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA). Wealthtrust Axiom Limited Liability Company stated it has 0.15% in W. R. Grace & Co (NYSE:GRA).
Investors sentiment increased to 0.97 in 2016 Q4. Its up 0.11, from 0.86 in 2016Q3. It improved, as 56 investors sold GME shares while 100 reduced holdings. 48 funds opened positions while 103 raised stakes. 98.80 million shares or 7.08% less from 106.32 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Central Financial Bank And invested 0.01% of its portfolio in GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME). National Bank Of Montreal Can owns 0% invested in GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME) for 37,630 shares. Gmt Corp accumulated 94,400 shares. Rhumbline Advisers invested in 186,085 shares or 0.01% of the stock. Rothschild Investment Corporation Il invested 0.05% of its portfolio in GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME). Narwhal Capital owns 0.12% invested in GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME) for 16,035 shares. Teacher Retirement Of Texas invested in 0% or 8,290 shares. Leuthold Ltd has invested 0.5% in GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME). Groesbeck Corp Nj reported 1.83% stake. Mutual Of America Capital Ltd Liability Com reported 79,095 shares or 0.04% of all its holdings. California Public Employees Retirement accumulated 465,803 shares. Citigroup owns 241,624 shares. Prudential Financial stated it has 0.1% in GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME). Northwestern Mutual Wealth reported 0% in GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME). Federated Investors Pa has invested 0.01% in GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME).
Among 20 analysts covering GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME), 11 have Buy rating, 1 Sell and 8 Hold. Therefore 55% are positive. GameStop Corp. had 63 analyst reports since August 6, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. Bank of America downgraded GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME) on Friday, March 24 to “Neutral” rating. The stock has “Outperform” rating by Robert W. Baird on Friday, August 26. Mizuho initiated it with “Buy” rating and $35 target in Friday, December 23 report. Benchmark maintained GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME) on Wednesday, November 2 with “Sell” rating. On Thursday, August 6 the stock rating was downgraded by Zacks to “Buy”. The firm has “Buy” rating by SunTrust given on Friday, August 14. The rating was upgraded by Zacks to “Hold” on Monday, August 17. The rating was downgraded by PiperJaffray on Wednesday, November 2 to “Neutral”. Credit Suisse maintained it with “Neutral” rating and $30 target in Monday, March 28 report. Telsey Advisory Group maintained GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME) rating on Thursday, November 3. Telsey Advisory Group has “Outperform” rating and $30 target.
Analysts await GameStop Corp. (NYSE:GME) to report earnings on August, 24. They expect $0.15 earnings per share, down 44.44% or $0.12 from last year’s $0.27 per share. GME’s profit will be $15.21M for 36.17 P/E if the $0.15 EPS becomes a reality. After $0.63 actual earnings per share reported by GameStop Corp. for the previous quarter, Wall Street now forecasts -76.19% negative EPS growth. 








