Leadership

 





















Executive Team and Investment Policy Committee
Our Investment Policy Committee, which is comprised of the most senior professionals at the firm, approves significant strategy recommendations and managers before they are implemented in any client portfolios. We have a bifurcated due diligence process in which both our manager team and compliance team do their own separate due diligence and report back to the Investment Policy Committee.  The safety of our clients’ assets is always our focus. Please contact us if you would like to discuss this in greater detail. 






